title: Creates the New York state governor's council on physical fitness, sports and health; establishes a fund for the council
summary: Creates the New York state governor's council on physical fitness, sports and health; establishes the membership of such council; creates the New York state governor's council on physical fitness, sports and health fund.
actClause: AN ACT to amend the public health law and the state finance law, in relation to creating the New York state governor's council on physical fitness, sports and health
